   <concept id="FAR_32_202_3" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">32.202-3</ph> Conducting market research about financing terms.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d2069e8" class="- topic/p ">Contract financing may be a subject included in the market research conducted in accordance with <xref href="Part_10.dita#FAR_Part_10"
                  base="i1114815"
                  outputclass="fm:Part"
                  class="- topic/xref ">partÂ  10</xref>. If market research for contract financing is conducted, the contracting officer should consider-</p>
         <ol id="d2039e22" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2064e15">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The extent to which other buyers provide contract financing for purchases in that market;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2064e20">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            The overall level of financing normally provided;</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2064e25">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(c)</ph>
						            The amount or percentages of any payments equivalent to commercial advance payments (see <xref href="32.202-2.dita#FAR_32_202_2"
                        base="i1083144"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.202-2</xref>);</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2064e33">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(d)</ph>
						            The basis for any payments equivalent to commercial interim payments (see <xref href="32.001.dita#FAR_32_001"
                        base="i1083391"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.001</xref>), as well as the frequency, and amounts or percentages; and</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d2064e41">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(e)</ph>
						            Methods of liquidation of contract financing payments and any special or unusual payment terms applicable to delivery payments (see <xref href="32.001.dita#FAR_32_001"
                        base="i1083391"
                        outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                        class="- topic/xref ">32.001</xref>).</p>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
</dita>
